# Email Attachment Processor Cron Job Configuration
# 
# This file shows example cron job entries for the email processor.
# Copy the relevant line to your crontab using: crontab -e
#
# Cron job format: minute hour day month weekday command
#
# Examples:
# Run every 15 minutes
# */15 * * * * /usr/bin/python3 /path/to/email_processor.py >> /var/log/email_processor.log 2>&1
#
# Run every hour at minute 0
# 0 * * * * /usr/bin/python3 /path/to/email_processor.py >> /var/log/email_processor.log 2>&1
#
# Run every 6 hours
# 0 */6 * * * /usr/bin/python3 /path/to/email_processor.py >> /var/log/email_processor.log 2>&1
#
# Run daily at 2:30 AM
# 30 2 * * * /usr/bin/python3 /path/to/email_processor.py >> /var/log/email_processor.log 2>&1
#
# Run every weekday at 9:00 AM
# 0 9 * * 1-5 /usr/bin/python3 /path/to/email_processor.py >> /var/log/email_processor.log 2>&1
#
# Run every Sunday at 3:00 AM
# 0 3 * * 0 /usr/bin/python3 /path/to/email_processor.py >> /var/log/email_processor.log 2>&1

# Recommended configuration for production:
# Run every 30 minutes during business hours (9 AM - 6 PM, Monday-Friday)
# */30 9-18 * * 1-5 /usr/bin/python3 /path/to/email_processor.py >> /var/log/email_processor.log 2>&1

# For testing purposes (runs every 5 minutes):
# */5 * * * * /usr/bin/python3 /path/to/email_processor.py >> /var/log/email_processor.log 2>&1
